Using .yml file:

TO Deployment : > kubectl apply -f <deploymentfile.yml>
eg:- kubectl apply -f deployment-node-app.yml

    > kubectl get deployment

    > kubectl get pods

To Service : > kubectl apply -f <servicefile.yml>
eg:- kubectl apply -f service-node-app.yml

    > minikube service service-my-node-app

To stop or, Delete: > kubectl delete -f <deploymrnfile.yml>
eg:- kubectl delete -f deployment-node-app.yml
